{"tid":866522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"梁振英一生總結　憶兩件事　","createTime":"2018-10-18T02:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-18T10:18:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7ed2138d68a27760e0b89eb6e0a7c62e684087bf","tid":866522,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181003/s00001/30e0d057fefb2f898733750f1127c154.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F30e0d057fefb2f898733750f1127c154.jpg&h=2812c62e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年是中華人民共和國建國69年，同時是改革開放40年，前特首梁振英接受中新社訪問時指，他參與改革開放的足迹「從南到北，從東到西」，「如果今日我要做一生的總結，參與國家改革開放是我一生最重要的兩件事之一，另一件就是親歷香港回歸祖國，籌組香港特別行政區」。<br />\n<br />\n作為國家改革開放參與者的梁振英又稱，「人生最有價值的地方並非銀行有多少存款，而是能為國家付出多少。今天香港的年輕人，機會更多，但凡事不能僅用商業角度看國家與香港的關係。」他強調，在要求國家給予「國民待遇」的同時，也應該承擔國民責任。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181003/s00001/1538538881873\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F1538538881873&d=u4stnqq8vOcMSVos4gNuvYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=abdbc116\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181003%2Fs00001%2F1538538881873&h=6ffb7e4e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181003/s00001/1538538881873</a>"},{"pid":"81bb275b2837e66b0f68b39897dca36364629eae","tid":866522,"uid":54359,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:46:28.000Z","msg":"咁你快d結啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e72f48e07cf96772e5c11e1cc4fca9aa87e11cb","tid":866522,"uid":82640,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T02:46:48.000Z","msg":"不要用銀行$50,000,000衡量他<br />\n<br />\n你就想<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />